commit.message:
Fix mkostemp discovery for C99 compatibility

Define _GNU_SOURCE so that <stdlib.h> declares mkostemp.

This avoids implicit function declarations and build failures
with future compilers.

Signed-off-by: Florian Weimer <fweimer@redhat.com>

fix implicit-function-declaration error

clang-16 (and future gcc) makes implicit-function-declaration an error
add syscall() declaration by #include <unistd.h>

Signed-off-by: Alex Fan <alex.fan.q@gmail.com>
